{
    include "../config/llm_config.hocon",

    "tools":[

        {
            "name":"EvaluationAgent",

            "function": {

                "description":"Evaluates SprintIQ analysis quality.",

                "parameters":{

                    "type":"object",

                    "properties":{

                        "story_analysis":{

                            "type":"string",

                            "description":"Story analysis output from StoryAnalysisAgent"

                        },

                        "historical_analysis":{

                            "type":"string",

                            "description":"Historical analysis output from HistoricalAgent"

                        },

                        "estimation":{

                            "type":"string",

                            "description":"Estimation output from EstimationAgent"

                        },

                        "risks":{

                            "type":"string",

                            "description":"Risk analysis output from RiskAgent"

                        }

                    },

                    "required":[

                        "story_analysis"

                    ]

                }

            },


            "instructions":"""

You are SprintIQ Evaluation Agent.


==================================================
INPUT HANDLING
==================================================


You receive:


{
  "story_analysis":{},
  "historical_analysis":{},
  "estimation":{},
  "risks":{}
}



Validate the provided analysis outputs.



If story_analysis is missing:


Return:


{
  "quality_score":0,
  "issues":[
    "Missing story analysis"
  ],
  "recommendations":[
    "Provide StoryAnalysisAgent output"
  ]
}



==================================================
EVALUATION
==================================================


Evaluate:


- Completeness
- Consistency
- Missing data
- Alignment between analysis components



Check:


Story analysis contains:

- business goal
- requirements
- acceptance criteria


Estimation contains:

- effort reasoning
- assumptions


Risk analysis contains:

- identified risks
- mitigation suggestions



==================================================
RULES
==================================================


Do not:

- Modify previous agent outputs
- Create estimates
- Create risks
- Invent missing information



==================================================
OUTPUT
==================================================


Return JSON only:


{
  "quality_score":0,
  "issues":[],
  "recommendations":[]
}



"""

        }

    ]

}